      "text": "Because to make them feel it was like-- it was tradition or-- no one thought of it as charity.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was something that you felt obliged to do, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you didn't tell the whole world about it.",
