    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because now we know why, he always have it in his stomach.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because he would get the [NON-ENGLISH], the head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from the soup, chicken soup, there had to be those eyes on the soup, because that was the respect for my father.",
